com.netapp.framework.http.client
Class HttpClient

java.lang.Object
  com.netapp.framework.http.client.HttpClient
Direct Known Subclasses:
XmlHttpClient
public abstract class HttpClient
extends Object

The HttpClient class can be used to make a HTTP connection and read from the connection
It uses UrlBuilder to construct the URL to establish the connection

Defaults
TimeOut : 5000ms / 5s
HTTP method : GET

Author:
hshashid
See Also:
UrlBuilder
